                "description": {
                    "value": "<p>The myceloid targets one creature affected by purple pox within 60 feet. That creature must attempt a DC 22 Will save. It is then temporarily immune to spore domination for 10 minutes.</p>\n<p><strong>Critical Success</strong> The target is unaffected.</p>\n<p><strong>Success</strong> Until the end of its next turn, the target is helpful to myceloids and can’t take hostile actions against them.</p>\n<p><strong>Failure</strong> As success, but for 1 minute.</p>\n<p><strong>Critical Failure</strong> As success, but until the purple pox is cured.</p>"
